8 the Housing and Community Services Department, for Multifamily Rental Housing Programs,
9 is increased by $150,000 for the administration of the Housing Opportunity, Longevity and
10 Durability Fund established by section 2 of this 2026 Act.
11 “SECTION 6. Notwithstanding any other law limiting expenditures, the limitation on
12 expenditures established by section 2 (3), chapter 584, Oregon Laws 2025, as the maximum
