15 opment for contract services, but excluding lottery funds and federal funds not described in
16 section 2, chapter 584, Oregon Laws 2025, collected or received by the Housing and Commu-
17 nity Services Department, for Multifamily Rental Housing Programs, is increased by $145,175
18 for the administration of the Housing Opportunity, Longevity and Durability Fund estab-
19 lished by section 2 of this 2026 Act.”.
20 In line 37, delete “6” and insert “7”.
